    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Chakra Control (Spirit)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 3 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 6</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 16 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 4 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 16</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You force the subject to obey one command per fifteen levels, from the list below. Subjects can make an additional save at a -4 penalty each round to end the effects.<br><br>- Approach: The subject moves towards you as quickly and directly as possible, taking no actions other than moving.<br>- Drop: On its turn, the subject drops whatever they are holding and cannot pick it back up until their next turn.<br>- Fall: The subject falls to the ground and remains @Condition[prone]{prone}, though it can take actions while remaining prone.<br>- Flee: As Approach, but it moves away from you instead.<br>- Halt: The subject stands in place and takes no actions, but will defend itself normally.</p>\n\n\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
